Abstract: Ann Powers reviews performance by rap group Arsonists; photo (S)
Snippet: Ann Powers reviews performance by rap group Arsonists; photo (S)
LeadParagraph: Q-Unique, one of the rappers in the Bushwick-based Arsonists crew, was home after a European tour, and he wasn't going to suffer a bland reception. ''You paid some good money to see a show,'' he urged the crowd Wednesday night at S.O.B.'s. ''Be part of the show!''

Headline.Main: Rappers Who Won't Let The Audience Be Lazy
